  <p>
    What a design-token standard covers. <strong>Protocol</strong> = fixed by the Design Tokens (DTCG &harr;
    CSS) contract; <strong>Compose</strong> = deferred to a neighbouring Web Everything standard;
    <strong>Member</strong> = realized as an intent dimension.
  </p>
